{"tid":1898041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實派一萬只不過係回水","createTime":"2020-02-26T03:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T04:17:46.000Z","uid":235527,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2fce79a85ca2343d14b2993ba5cddb393ada4b","tid":1898041,"uid":235527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"仲要得個雞水咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港交左咁多多稅政府都冇作為不特只仲要用啲錢黎打壓香港人。<br />\n<br />\n犧牲左咁多手足都係得個1萬咋，一條人命都唔止啦<br />\n民主自由更加係無價。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母呢個時候仲當香港人係比錢就得既低等動物，仲要得個一萬。咁多年交埋啲稅都唔止啦。<br />\n<br />\n呢世都唔原諒港共政權 派幾多錢都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢突然咁大方咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3471bd3d924993a231d7924eea64b2bbf983473a","tid":1898041,"uid":235527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"係時候用啲錢繼續支持黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d69b733c63014761cdd47d8d69979ce84bc591","tid":1898041,"uid":235527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3471bd3d924993a231d7924eea64b2bbf983473a","tid":1898041,"uid":235527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"係時候用啲錢繼續支持黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:43:09.000Z","msg":"大大力g持！"},{"pid":"6ca7954f4c266f6c874c045a2814506643a23441","tid":1898041,"uid":235527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"呢世都唔會原諒港共政權 話之佢跪地求饒 何況而家家淨係派得個一皮"},{"pid":"e4abb709c0c9f1cb54519884d459b2820be1e0e9","tid":1898041,"uid":235527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"錢照袋 態度照舊"},{"pid":"4c9c046e76051b7db62d65575f49d748486e768d","tid":1898041,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3471bd3d924993a231d7924eea64b2bbf983473a","tid":18980